Cabot Wealth Management, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 22, 2017 10:31 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Cabot Wealth Management, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Cabot Wealth Management, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. The firm also provides financial planning services, trust and endowment management services, and wealth management services, including estate plan reviews, tax planning, and tax preparation and to its clients. It primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. The firm also caters to individuals, corporate pension and profit sharing plans, charitable and non-profit organizations, corporations and other business entities, foundations, endowments, municipalities, private investment funds, trust programs, and other U.S. institutions. It manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. The fi...
Cabot Wealth Management, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. The firm also provides financial planning services, trust and endowment management services, and wealth management services, including estate plan reviews, tax planning, and tax preparation and to its clients. It primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. The firm also caters to individuals, corporate pension and profit sharing plans, charitable and non-profit organizations, corporations and other business entities, foundations, endowments, municipalities, private investment funds, trust programs, and other U.S. institutions. It manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. It also invests in cash and alternative asset classes, including gold, commodities, and natural resource-based funds. To make its equity investments, the firm invests in both U.S. and foreign stocks, mutual funds, and exchange traded funds. It employs a combination of fundamental and technical analysis to create its portfolios. The firm was formerly known as Cabot Money Management, Inc. Cabot Wealth Management, Inc. was founded in 1983 and is based in Salem, Massachusetts with an additional office in Boston, Massachusetts.
Detailed Description


